title: Week 12 preview & Chiefs vs. Raiders recap
itunes:title: Week 12 preview & Chiefs vs. Raiders recap
description:
A room with some heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- preview every Week 12 game on the NFL schedule and recap "Thursday Night Football" between the Chiefs and Raiders.
